room_title: Escape room "Spy Game" by Escape Room Lafayette in Lafayette
review: We just left from doing the Spy Room! There were 4 of us, and we escaped with 1:31 to spare! It was fantastic but challenging! Would definitely recommend to others, so addicting!

room_title: Escape room "Spy Game" by Escape Room Lafayette in Lafayette
review: We went through the Spy room last night. I went into this doubtful that I would enjoy it. I had an amazing time! We can not stop talking about how much fun we had! Can not wait to do another room. The employees are wonderful and so very helpful!
